      {
        "children": [
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "If you wanted to be like Agent 007, Neiman Marcus worked with BMW to create a launch edition of the Z3 patterned after the one James Bond drove in ",
