            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "When the Italian sedan was launched, Neiman Marcus helped Maserati celebrate with the first version of the Quattroporte available in the United States. Each one cost $125,000 and quantities were limited to 60 total. The red paint was exclusive.",
