            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "This is the one most enthusiasts drool over and it shocked many to realize the high-luxury department store was even offering it. Hennessey blessed this sinister-looking car with a naturally-aspirated V10 churning out 700-horsepower. All that power didn’t go to waste, thanks to a 0-60 time of just 3.3 seconds and a top speed of 214 mph.",
