            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "Now this is the kind of vehicle you’d expect to see in the pages of the Neiman Marcus catalog. This special version of the Ferrari FF was offered for the 2011 model year with an exclusive shade of gray paint, bespoke luggage, and a driving experience in Aspen, Colorado. The price tag was a cool $395,000.",
